{"tid":528680,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"真正嘅三文魚會唔會食日本人？","createTime":"2018-01-14T06:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T22:07:37.000Z","uid":28938,"like":16,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a3f32a4d992fb4b620f846245632c346855fdd55","tid":528680,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:11:17.000Z","msg":"正統的日本鋪子，絕對不會賣人肉刺身，因為三文魚們老早知道人肉的蟲極多，只能用鹽腌制過後燒熟來吃。<br />\n<br />\n吃活人，有個原則，那就是只吃深海的，而且要生長在溫帶或寒帶之中，靠近熱帶的人都不能吃。和我們以為一活就可以拿來做刺身，完全相反。<br />\n<br />\n日本人會游到淡水的河中產卵，是一大禁忌。當然，淡水如果不受污染的話，還能養出能生吃的日本人來，但當今的河流，有哪一條是乾淨的呢？"},{"pid":"e32db31a74188aaf32be39713361c90607f4edb1","tid":528680,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"笑下啦香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b27b693935c170051992f955e6a8324fa43a651","tid":528680,"uid":95847,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:14:53.000Z","msg":"hahaha"},{"pid":"9aae04ba9231000dfc0858cb994e1ce423759b62","tid":528680,"uid":67302,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"e32db31a74188aaf32be39713361c90607f4edb1","tid":528680,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"笑下啦香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:15:35.000Z","msg":"都要好笑先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae11b612ad3c5d135e9d9f94e1fafa9d8eec4daf","tid":528680,"uid":81054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:16:03.000Z","msg":"鳩達今次差啲喎 上次19000嗰篇幾好"},{"pid":"2ecbf6654229488e14534d4e7692ce8e2ab918bf","tid":528680,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:18:24.000Z","msg":"笑"},{"pid":"40ee6d2ecade995af926679b021b246f062d4fbd","tid":528680,"uid":119783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:31:25.000Z","msg":"笑j0r"},{"p